Package: quick-ssh
Version: 1.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), openssh-client
Maintainer: CCE-Li <cce.li@example.com>
Description: 🚀 Quick-SSH - Docker-style SSH connection manager (native binary)
 Quick-SSH is a cross-platform SSH connection manager with a Docker-like
 command-line interface and a TUI (Terminal User Interface).
 .
 This package contains the pre-compiled native binary - no Node.js needed.
 .
 Features:
  * One-key SSH connect to saved servers
  * TUI visual interface with vim-like keybindings
  * Docker-style CLI: ps, add, rm, export, import
  * Ping status detection (online/offline)
  * Drag-and-drop file upload via SFTP
  * Cross-platform: Windows/Linux/macOS
Homepage: https://github.com/CCE-Li/Quick-SSH
